<section xml:id="C29.S22">
<title>Software</title>         
<para xml:id="C29.S22.p1">

</para>
 
<para xml:id="C29.S22.p2">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="1" xml:id="C29.S22.p2.s1">
In this section we provide links to the research literature describing the implementation of algorithms in software for the evaluation of functions described in this chapter.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="2" sentence-num-in-section="2" xml:id="C29.S22.p2.s2">
Included also are links to software provided by the auther.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="3" sentence-num-in-section="3" xml:id="C29.S22.p2.s3">
For other software see the Software Index.
</sentence>

</para>
 
<subsection xml:id="C29.S22.SS1">
<title>Lamé Functions</title>         
<para xml:id="C29.S22.SS1.p1">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="4" xml:id="C29.S22.SS1.p1.s1">
The following Maple programs were provided by the author.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="2" sentence-num-in-section="5" xml:id="C29.S22.SS1.p1.s2">
LA1: Eigenvalues for Lamé functions.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="3" sentence-num-in-section="6" xml:id="C29.S22.SS1.p1.s3">
LA2: Lamé functions.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="4" sentence-num-in-section="7" xml:id="C29.S22.SS1.p1.s4">
LA5: Coefficients <Math mode="inline" xml:id="C29.S22.I1.i3.p1.m1">\tau_{j}</Math> of the asymptotic expansions for the eigenvalues of the Lamé functions; see §29.7(i).
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="5" sentence-num-in-section="8" xml:id="C29.S22.SS1.p1.s5">
Precision in LA1 and LA2 is adjustable.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="6" sentence-num-in-section="9" xml:id="C29.S22.SS1.p1.s6">
Program LA5 uses symbolic algebra.
</sentence>

</para>
 
</subsection>
 
